          },
          "activation_name": "Eagle\u2019s Cry",
          "effect": "The musket unleashes a piercing sound wave in a 70-foot line. Each creature in the area takes 8d10 sonic damage with a DC 30 basic Fortitude save. A creature that critically fails its save is also deafened. If the *screaming pinion* has a *+3 potency* rune, the DC increases to 35, and the damage increases to 10d10.",
