    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This *+2 greater striking flintlock musket* is an innovation of the Platinum Wing, and possession of one by a civilian is a high crime in Andoran. The gun\u2019s secret is the chip of a warshard used as the hammer in the striking mechanism.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
